					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="skills__content-column">
				<div class="skills__item media">
					<div class="sprite html media__figure"></div>
					<div class="media__body-container">
						<h3 class="media__body-heading">HTML5</h3>
						<p class="media__body-content">Semantic, accessible markup, new attributes and elements, cross-browser polyfills.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="skills__item media">
					<div class="sprite css media__figure"></div>
					<div class="media__body-container">
						<h3 class="media__body-heading">CSS3</h3>
						<p class="media__body-content">CSS3 selectors, cross-browser polyfills, SASS, LESS, naming conventions (OOCSS, SMACSS, BEM), responsive design, media queries, sprites.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="skills__item media">
					<div class="sprite github media__figure"></div>
					<div class="media__body-container">
						<h3 class="media__body-heading">Git/Github</h3>
						<p class="media__body-content">Peer review via pull requests, branching.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
